== 觀測 ==
[[英国|英国]][[皇家學會|皇家學會]]和[[英國皇家天文學會|英國皇家天文學會]]組成的聯合常設日食委員會到荷屬東印度[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]島西岸的[[巴東_(西蘇門答臘省)|巴東]]觀測了日全食。5月18日當天日出後天氣不錯，但日食開始後雲逐漸變多，到全食階段，一直有雲籠罩著太阳，且有變厚的趨勢，透過雲層看太阳越來越困難。<ref>{{cite journal|author=H. F. Newall|title=Total Solar Eclipse of 1901, May 17-18. Preliminary Report of the Observations Made at Ayer Karoe, Sawah Loento, Sumatra|url=http://www.jstor.org/stable/116302|publisher=[[皇家學會|皇家學會]]|volume=69|year=1901–1902|pages=209-234|accessdate=2016-04-08|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009062110/https://www.jstor.org/stable/116302|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>[[美国|美国]][[利克天文台|利克天文台]]的觀測隊也在巴東觀測了日全食。<ref>{{cite web|author=C. D. Perrine|title=THE LICK OBSERVATORY-CROCKER EXPEDITION TO OBSERVE THE TOTAL SOLAR ECLIPSE OF 1901, MAY 17-18|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|url=https://archive.org/details/jstor-40668190|pages=187-204|date=1901-12-01|issn=00046280|accessdate=2016-04-08}}{{en}}</ref>

